{"tid":371562,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"(適合男士睇)(變大變細loli) 29歲單身冒險家的日常","createTime":"2017-08-23T18:25:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-14T13:41:07.000Z","uid":6327,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"07b83990e61681e4376a59105b5c5558f3b77fa6","tid":371562,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T18:25:46.000Z","msg":"套野係講個29歲寡佬執到個細路女(?)<br />\n然後久唔久帶去打怪同一d on99既日常<br />\n越後就越有d色情neta妓院啊呢d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日以為自己好好抽但好廢既loli<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/24/021153_47c6dd7df00b2dc28cdf497e3eadafdb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F24%2F021153_47c6dd7df00b2dc28cdf497e3eadafdb.jpg&h=bb0aaca4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n主角開始懷疑佢既身世...原來係識得夜晚會變成大人(種族唔劇透了)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/24/021548_8dff89a2a1bf0104adb521d5093e05f2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F24%2F021548_8dff89a2a1bf0104adb521d5093e05f2.jpg&h=7739a364&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日常得黎不乏一d令人感到小小心酸既環節<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/24/021722_69a996c691e42d65c773a99b6fad34ad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F24%2F021722_69a996c691e42d65c773a99b6fad34ad.jpg&h=9f62d5cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/24/021733_80bc7ae28aa9f06d764565b44c4229a0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F24%2F021733_80bc7ae28aa9f06d764565b44c4229a0.jpg&h=b99aa72e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/24/021741_fb413ed935fe416f9d9a6c553e040eb6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F24%2F021741_fb413ed935fe416f9d9a6c553e040eb6.jpg&h=7d7afc8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n淫魔唔會染性病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/24/022238_fbca3e5baea73f65b5547296db0f6dd1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F24%2F022238_fbca3e5baea73f65b5547296db0f6dd1.jpg&h=4b41954f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n小朋友好黑暗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/24/022250_b82383ed884bcbd2b836d862f7ff984f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F24%2F022250_b82383ed884bcbd2b836d862f7ff984f.jpg&h=dc55f377&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f0f56e4e9886ab38a6fa545d9b2fdf9e91f1278c","tid":371562,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T18:52:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb2925bf3e1abb34ae6738aa6d36f8c24f65d7f0","tid":371562,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T00:36:33.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"64b52cc435ee7c15bb9e0e18c463440033a2ea75","tid":371562,"uid":38540,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T03:25:55.000Z","msg":"名都冇"},{"pid":"19645a2feadb8e6c29e6153813f29699e050efb9","tid":371562,"uid":9247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T03:29:33.000Z","msg":"名呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3bcd26859f039a46fd83d9cd9691146bb3b55e9","tid":